Floy Privacy Policy

Effective Date: [Feb, 23, 2026]
Floy (“we,” “our,” or “us”) values your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our mobile application (“the App”).

1. Information We Collect
1.1 Account Information
 When you sign in with Sign in with Apple, we may receive limited information such as your name and email address (if you choose to share it). This is used only for authentication and user identification within the app.
1.2 User-Generated Data
 When you enter your income or expense data in Floy, this information is securely stored on our database to provide syncing and history features. However, when user wants to set up app data, all data can be deleted. 

1.3 Guest Mode
 If you use the app in Guest Mode, we do not collect or store any personal information.
 All data created in Guest Mode is saved locally and deleted when the app is removed.

2. How We Use Information
We use the collected data only to:
Provide and maintain the app’s features (such as income tracking, summaries, and sync).


Identify and authenticate users.


Improve stability and fix technical issues.


We do not use or sell your information for marketing or advertising.

3. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not share, sell, or rent your data to third parties.
 We also do not use any third-party analytics or advertising SDKs.
 Your data is only accessible by Floy for service maintenance and troubleshooting purposes.

4. Data Storage and Security
User data is securely stored in our database and protected with industry-standard encryption.
 Only authorized personnel can access it when necessary to maintain the app.
 We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or loss.

5. Payments
Floy does not process or collect any payment information.
 There are no in-app purchases or subscription features at this time.

6. Your Rights
You can request deletion of your data at any time by contacting us at the email below or deleting your account in the app (if available).
 Once your account is deleted, all associated data will be permanently removed from our servers.

7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
 If changes are made, we will update the “Effective Date” at the top of this page.

